<Base title="About" description="Learn about Summit Ledger Books and our mission to provide reliable bookkeeping services for small businesses.">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="section-heading">About Summit Ledger Books</h1>

    <img src="/images/austin-headshot.png" alt="Austin, founder of Summit Ledger Books" class="about-headshot" />

    <div class="prose">
      <p>Summit Ledger Books was founded with a simple belief: every small business deserves accurate, affordable bookkeeping. Too many business owners spend their evenings wrestling with spreadsheets instead of spending time with family or planning their next big move.</p>

      <p>We started Summit Ledger Books to change that. Our team of experienced bookkeepers partners with small businesses to keep their financial records organized, accurate, and up to date — so owners can focus on what they do best.</p>

      <h2>Our Values</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Accuracy</strong> — Your books need to be right. We double-check every entry and reconciliation.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparency</strong> — No hidden fees, no surprises. You'll always know exactly what you're paying for.</li>
        <li><strong>Reliability</strong> — We meet every deadline, every month. Your books are never behind.</li>
        <li><strong>Simplicity</strong> — We explain your finances in plain language, not accounting jargon.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Who We Serve</h2>

      <p>We specialize in working with small businesses, freelancers, and solopreneurs. Whether you're a consultant, contractor, e-commerce seller, or local shop owner, we've got the experience to handle your books.</p>

      <p>Ready to take bookkeeping off your plate? <a href="https://calendly.com/summit-ledger-books/consultation">Book a free consultation</a> for a free consultation.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
